title: Dublin's electropunk three-piece YARD perform Live on KEXP from Trans Musicales

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents YARD performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 06, 2024. 

Songs:
Call 00:00
Big Shoes 03:30
Bend 06:57
Trevor 10:02
Lawmaker 16:18
Sunlight 20:36

George Ryan - Beats, Synth
Emmet White - Beats, Vocals
Daniel Malone - Guitar

Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Audio Mixer: James Eager

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann
